title: American Horror Story Season 10 Episode 1 Cape Fear Synopsis and Review
author: MaryGirl Moody
comment: This season has given me The Shining/ 30 days of night vibes.
I loved the atmosphere, the soundtrack, the characters, all of it. Very strong start, and looking forward to hearing you discuss this season, Mary!
I like how this cinematography has changed.
I feel like the screenplay script Harry is writing while on the pill is going to be the plot for Death Valley! that would be a cool twist/transition into part 2 of this season
Fin and Evan are so dreamy!!!!!! I love the “pale folks” big shoulder over coats!!!!!  Thanks for the review!!!!!
